The paper focuses on interactive recommender systems, which are commonly studied in the information retrieval (IR) field (cs.IR). The proposed model also involves machine learning techniques such as Meta-Path and Attention-GRU, which are often used in the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper deals with personalized questions and user feedback, which are relevant to the sub-fields of cybersecurity (cs.CY) and social media (cs.SI).
